저도 telnet를 통하여 천리안에 접속하면서 유사한 문제를 겪었는데 
han.sys.linux에서 어떤분이 binary mode telnet를 권고하더군요.
It solved the problem.  Unfortuantely, however, not all telnet
programs support (or allow) the binary mode. One I am currently
using is one in Linux slackware package. 

In case you aren't familiar with....
  1. make a connection, and login.
  2. escape (ctrl + ^ + ]).
  3. type "set bin" in, then press enter key.

Good luck.

