You need to use the '-r' option to less, so that it does not strip the
8th bit of the hangul characters.  You can make this automatic, by
setting an environment variable named LESS.  I use:

setenv LESS "-ficesr"

in csh. For sh/ksh, you would use

LESS="-ficesr" ; export LESS

-jem

